    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/893f2080-f656-463b-a4ef-fe1db7e9bc4f/resource/69a7105e-2b37-426b-b803-44cd2c07f2e7>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/893f2080-f656-463b-a4ef-fe1db7e9bc4f/resource/8aa2ad77-d405-45e2-bf47-e0c9f7a94207>;
