    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://stuns.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/14> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://stuns.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/66>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://stuns.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/18>, <https://stuns.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/16>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/provenance> "STUNS i samverkan med Region Uppsala"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2019-08-14"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://energiportalregionuppsala.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2020-10-14"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "List of solar power plants at Region Uppsala real estates"@en, "Förteckning över solcellsanläggningar vid Region Uppsalas fastigheter"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#versionNotes> "Tredje utgåvan med enbart övergripande information, ny version kommer när nya anläggningar installerats. Den detaljerade informationen på växelriktarnivå samt solpanelsnivå har flyttats till en ny datamängd, se Relaterad resurs. I denna version finns tre (3) nya solelanläggningar presenterade."@sv, "Third version, now ony containing the overall info of the solar power plants. The in depth, detailed info is published in a separate data source, see Related resource. New versions released when new solar plants have been installed - here three (3) new sites are presented."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENER>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "New version october 2020";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__81120.
_:b0__81120 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2020-10-14"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://stuns.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/14> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>, <http://entryscape.com/terms/ServedByDataService>
}

